'''Escort Carriers (CVE)''' are Light Carriers (CVL) with a base ASW stat. They are able to perform [[Combat/Opening_Anti-Submarine_Warfare|Opening ASW]] when meeting certain conditions and are able to be placed in the main fleet of a [[Combined_Fleet#Transport_Escort_Force|Transport Combined Fleet]].

The following are only considered CVE on remodel:
* Taiyou
* Ryuuhou Kai Ni/E 
* Zuihou Kai Ni B